r />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/11/162419_41c521814f38e90ba9a0f7d97c9db7e7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F11%2F162419_41c521814f38e90ba9a0f7d97c9db7e7.jpg&h=45f6928c&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n打FIFA就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab8644f65ffcdbf7e2e48f2a98abc623e2694395","tid":395891,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T11:26:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢幾勁，暫時英超三大標王都對板</blockquote><br />\n有你幫手更上一層樓"}]}